# Leaflet Heatmap Widget
# Interactive heatmap visualization component for web mapping applications

Widget Name: Leaflet Heatmap Widget
Version: 2.1.0
Description: Interactive heatmap visualization component for web mapping applications.
Author: HaritaHive Team

Files included:
- heatmap-widget.js (main widget script)
- heatmap-widget.css (styling)
- examples/ (usage examples)
- README.md (documentation)

Usage:
1. Include the JavaScript and CSS files in your project
2. Initialize the heatmap widget with your data
3. Customize appearance and behavior using the provided options

Example:
var heatmap = new HeatmapWidget({
  container: 'map',
  data: yourDataPoints,
  radius: 20
});